		{"id":"7xd3HaKYVjiamWnAGR4l-1543","x":1550,"y":360,"width":887,"height":924,"type":"text","text":"On progressivism\n\nTerms:\nProgress stems from the belief that our current circumstance is not good enough, driving us to explore and innovate for to make things better.\n\nTrails:How our current circumstances aren't good enough, and what better looks like, and how to get there are the trials of the progress. \n\nTensions:\nProgress is inherently fractured, different people will fall on different parts of the Progressive v Conservative spectrum on different issues. \nOpinion on how progressive or conser..."},
