		{"id":"uMTBItHwGZwq3fhviun5-1640","x":6280,"y":-19148,"width":560,"height":710,"type":"text","text":"Primary Spectrums\nOn progress. Not every change is an improvement. But every improvement is a change\nProgressive vs Conservative\nProgressive[1] - the more progressive you are, the more you are willing to risk or sacrifice what we have for a chance at a better future, and the more open you are to anything that might mean better.\nConservative - the more conservative you are the more you are unwilling to risk what we have for a chance at a better future, and are more skeptical or resistant of anyth..."},
